source.name: List of Public Elementary and Secondary Schools: 1986-Present
source.description: The primary purposes of the Public Elementary/Secondary School Universe Survey are: (a) to provide a complete listing of all public elementary and secondary schools in the country; and (b) to provide basic information and descriptive statistics on all schools, their students, and their teachers.
